            <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Industry:</strong> Press Manufacturing</li>
              <li><strong>Size:</strong> One of the largest press manufacturers globally</li>
              <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Slow quote generation process</li>
              <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> Dramatically reduced cycle times</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Koenig & Bauer Group, one of the largest press manufacturers in the world, faced significant challenges with their quote generation process. The manual system required weeks to generate customer quotes, creating bottlenecks that limited their ability to respond quickly to customer inquiries and compete effectively in fast-moving markets.
          </p>
          
