            The Ultimus automation solution transformed their quote generation process by automating complex calculations, integrating pricing data, and streamlining approvals. This automation reduced their cycle times from weeks to hours, allowing quotes to reach customers in only 1 day instead of the previous multi-week timeline.
          </p>
        </div>
        
